text: Johan Nicolai Trock Hartling (born 17 January 1994 in Hørsholm) is a Danish hurdler. He established several national records on 400 m hurdles, the last one of 50.01, finishing third at 2019 European Team Championships. ==References== ==External links== *IAAF Athlete’s profile Category:Danish male hurdlers Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:European Games competitors for Denmark Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2019 European Games Category:People from Hørsholm Municipality
